### Analysis of the Main Target Image

#### Structure 1 (Left)
- **Base Layer**: 
  - Two vertical green rectangular blocks, side by side, forming the central support.
  - A horizontal yellow rectangular block at the bottom.

- **Middle Layer**:
  - Two horizontal yellow rectangular blocks, forming a perimeter around the vertical green blocks.

- **Upper Layer**:
  - Two vertical red cylindrical blocks on top of the middle yellow blocks.
  - A horizontal yellow rectangular block placed on top of the red cylinders.

- **Top Structure**:
  - A single red triangular block on top of the horizontal yellow block.

#### Structure 2 (Right)
- **Base Layer**:
  - Two red horizontal cylinders parallel and side by side.
  
- **Upper Layer**:
  - One yellow rectangular block placed horizontally on top of the two red cylinders.
